I see Jenny Strebe who cuts and Veronica Peebles who colors.
They are AMAZING!
I am so glad they opened Salon Stylush, it is the perfect size (not too huge and crazy) and it is so modern & cute!
Jenny is an amazing hair stylist with the accolades to prove it (she styles hair for fashion shows, magazines, television, etc).
Jenny has been cutting my hair for years and she is super sweet and super talented.
I trust her with my hair, no question, and recommend her highly.
Also, she has a talent for men's hair as well.
She cuts my husband's hair and that is one of his best qualities (I'd say!).
There are so many men out there with bad hair - Jenny knows how to make it work for men!
