Just as adorable as the salon are the ladies who own and operate it.
I have followed Jenny from the last two salons she has been at will continue to do as as long as I am in Arizona.
Cuts, styling and color are what I see her for and no joke I get compliments ALL the time.
We've played around with length and color over the years and I have never had a bad visit and it always looks natural.
I trust Jenny completely with whatever she does.
I'm so excited to have her do hair for my wedding in October!
I know I'm going tho have "kick ass" hair!
The space is fun and inviting and they always make you feel welcome.
The decor is unique and funky...love the curtains!
All of the ladies here are up on the most current trends in hair so you'll never have an "old lady" hair style.
Go visit the ladies of Salon Stylush!

